### ============================================
### FINAL TESTING - ONLINE MARKETPLACE API
### ============================================

### 1. CREATE A NEW USER (Public)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "finalizer",
  "email": "finalizer@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Final",
  "lastName": "Test",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890",
  "address": "123 Test Street",
  "city": "Addis Ababa",
  "country": "Ethiopia"
}

### 2. CREATE CATEGORY (Admin - Ebise_Gutema)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "description": "Electronic devices and accessories"
}

### 3. CREATE PRODUCT (Admin - Ebise_Gutema)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance laptop",
  "price": 999.99,
  "stockQuantity": 10,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/laptop.jpg",
  "categoryIds": [1]
}

### 4. GET ALL PRODUCTS (Public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### 5. GET ALL CATEGORIES (Public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories

### 6. PLACE ORDER (User - finaluser)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Basic ZmluYWx1c2VyOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD"
}

### 7. GET ORDER BY ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1
Authorization: Basic ZmluYWx1c2VyOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz

### 8. GET ALL USERS (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz

### 9. UPDATE ORDER STATUS (Admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/status?status=SHIPPED
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz

### 10. GET USER ORDERS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/user/1
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz

### ============================================
### EDGE CASE TESTS
### ============================================

### 11. STOCK VALIDATION (Try to order more than available)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Basic ZmluYWx1c2VyOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 100
    }
  ],
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD"
}

### 12. PRICE VALIDATION (Create product with negative price)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Product",
  "description": "This should fail",
  "price": -10.00,
  "stockQuantity": 5,
  "categoryIds": [1]
}

### 13. NON-EXISTENT PRODUCT (Order with invalid product ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Basic ZmluYWx1c2VyOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 999,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD"
}

### 14. NON-EXISTENT USER
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/99
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz

### 15. NON-EXISTENT ORDER
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/9999
Authorization: Basic ZmluYWx1c2VyOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz

### 16. UNAUTHORIZED ACCESS (No credentials)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/status?status=SHIPPED

### 17. MISSING REQUIRED FIELDS (Create product without name)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Authorization: Basic RWJpc2VfR3V0ZW1hOnBhc3N3b3JkMTIz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Missing name and price"
}

### 18. DUPLICATE USER (Try to create existing user)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "finaluser",
  "email": "final@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Duplicate",
  "lastName": "User"
}